Class NumberSetPermutationEnumeration

java.lang.Object
  com.espertech.esper.collection.NumberSetPermutationEnumeration
All Implemented Interfaces:
Enumeration<int[]>
public class NumberSetPermutationEnumeration
extends Object
implements Enumeration<int[]>

Based on the PermutationEnumeration this enumeration provides, among a set of supplied integer values, all permutations of order these values can come in, ie. Example: {0, 2, 3} results in 6 enumeration values ending in {3, 2, 0}.
